Simple Queries:
    --> done by using SELECT function

format:

SELECT
    <column name1>,
    <column name 2>,
    ...,
    <column name n>
FROM
    <table name1>,
    <table name2>,
    ...,
    <table name n>
WHERE
    <conditions that you want to add
        mathematical conditions
        logical conditions
        logical operators
        string conditions
        ... etc
    >;


example:

SELECT
    firstName, mi, lastName
FROM
    Student
WHERE deptId = 'CS';